<p>This tool allows you to add or edit a heading content item, when adding a 
new heading item you define the heading text, margin values, container width 
and also the heading type, the heading type dictates the styling.</p>

<p>The margin and width values will be defaulted based upon the size of the 
page container, the values will also be validated when the tool is being 
processed, you cannot add a content container which is larger than the page 
container.</p>

<p>In edit mode you will be able to define the styling for the content 
container and also the formatting for the heading, this will override the 
styles defined for the selected heading type. The styles for each of the 
heading types can be updated in the 
<a href="/content/settings/headings">Content manager settings.</a></p>